<DOC><DOCNO> DOE1-34-0895 </DOCNO><TEXT>This paper outlines the environmental policy statement adopted by 3M Canada,Inc. that also carries over to their waste handling strategy. Both policiesaim to minimize waste and pollution at the source. To do this the companyhas implemented the methodology of developing non-polluting productsor reformulating existing products, modifying production operations,redesigning manufacturing equipment, and recycling waste products. Alloperating divisions of the company are encouraged to submit pollutionprevention projects, which are evaluated before implementation. Examplesof successful projects are included.</TEXT></DOC>